SCOPE OF THE RESULT

The repository proves a certified finite positivity band and an analytic
bounded-radius obstruction for its fixed cross-endpoint polynomial hierarchy.
It does not claim a proof of the Riemann Hypothesis or a new record for
finite-height verification.
